Title: Coyote 36-Inch Built-In Pellet Grill - C1P36
Description:
Key FeaturesEasy to use digital touch screen interface gives you precise control304 grade stainless steel components for reliable outdoor performanceFront loading pellet hopper makes refueling easy and convenientIncluded interchangeable burn pot grates allow you to easily go from smoking to searingIncludes 3 temperature probes for monitoring foods as they cookThe Coyote pellet grill brings the functionality and luxury of an indoor appliance to your backyard. This 36-inch, built-in pellet grill features intuitive digital touch screen controls and features that help take the guesswork out of grilling. Heavy-duty 304 stainless steel construction ensures years of outdoor use. The double-walled hood with a gasket keeps heat contained for added efficiency and more consistent grilling temperatures, it also has a built in spring mechanism for easy opening, and a wind-guard to protect against drafts. The front-loading hopper provides an easier way to add fuel and holds up to 15 lbs of pellets at a time. The Coyote Smart Drop pellet feed system features dual augers and is compatible with any flavored wood pellets. Heavy duty, laser-cut 304 stainless steel cooking grates provide extra surface contact for great sear marks. The Coyote Versa-Rack system allows you to expand the warming rack for additional cooking surface area. This pellet grill easily converts from smoking to searing mode with the included interchangeable burn pot grates and removal tool. A dual fan convection system allows precise temperature control ranging from 175 to 700 degrees Fahrenheit, depending on which burn pot grate is in use. Three temperature probes are included for easy monitoring of internal food temperatures using the digital control panel. Interior grill lighting and an LED temperature probe port light allow you to grill in any lighting.Legal disclaimers and warnings

Title: Coyote 28-Inch Pellet Grill - C1P28-FS
Description:
Key FeaturesEasy to use digital touch screen interface gives you precise control304 grade stainless steel components for reliable outdoor performanceFront loading pellet hopper makes refueling easy and convenientIncluded interchangeable burn pot grates allow you to easily go from smoking to searingIncludes 3 temperature probes for monitoring foods as they cookThe Coyote pellet grill brings the functionality and luxury of an indoor appliance to your backyard. This 28-inch, freestanding pellet grill features intuitive digital touch screen controls and features that help take the guesswork out of grilling. Heavy-duty 304 stainless steel construction ensures years of outdoor use. The double-walled hood with a gasket keeps heat contained for added efficiency and more consistent grilling temperatures, it also has a built in spring mechanism for easy opening, and a wind-guard to protect against drafts. The front-loading hopper provides an easier way to add fuel and holds up to 12 lbs of pellets at a time. The Coyote Smart Drop pellet feed system features dual augers and is compatible with any flavored wood pellets. Heavy duty, laser-cut 304 stainless steel cooking grates provide extra surface contact for great sear marks. The Coyote Versa-Rack system allows you to expand the warming rack for additional cooking surface area. This pellet grill easily converts from smoking to searing mode with the included interchangeable burn pot grates and removal tool. A dual fan convection system allows precise temperature control ranging from 175 to 650 degrees Fahrenheit, depending on which burn pot grate is in use. Three temperature probes are included for easy monitoring of internal food temperatures using the digital control panel. Interior grill lighting and an LED temperature probe port light allow you to grill in any lighting. The grill cart features two drawers with dual removable drip trays for easier cleanup, as well as two large storage drawers to keep your grilling tools and accessories handy.Legal disclaimers and warnings

Key FeaturesTwo independent heat zones allow you to cook multiple types of food at one timeHeavy gauge stainless steel cooking surface for even heating and cleanupLED safety lit grill knobs indicate when gas supply is onHeavy-duty 304 stainless steel construction for durability and longevityIncluded stainless steel lid protects flat top grill when not in useMerging durable construction, design and value, the Coyote flat top gas grill will make a statement in any outdoor kitchen. This 30-Inch flat top gas grill features two u-shaped stainless steel burners rated for up to 36,000 BTUs. A heavy gauge stainless steel cooking surface ensures even heating. Cleanup is also simple with a removable grease tray. This natural gas griddle is made entirely of 304 grade stainless steel for long lasting durability in outdoor environments. The 400 square inch cooking surface is covered by two independent heat zones, allowing you to cook simultaneously at different temperatures. Constructed with safety in mind, LED lights in the knob bezels will glow orange when the burner is lit. If the light turns blue while in use, this indicates there is no longer a flame present. The freestanding cart includes two fold down side shelves which add valuable workspace while grilling. Two heavy duty drawers on the left side of the cart provide storage space for gilling accessories. The grill cart also features wheel casters for easy mobility in your outdoor space. Includes a stainless steel cover and requires a 120V connection.Legal disclaimers and warnings

Title: Coyote 36-Inch Stainless Steel Outdoor Hood Insert With Internal 1200 CFM Blower Motor
Description:
